{"tid":1655501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳彥霖單野同早幾年林子健案有D似","createTime":"2019-10-15T05:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T01:07:14.000Z","uid":111007,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"12c18d5927fc4aa873c89090a03d648d788576a3","tid":1655501,"uid":111007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:53:36.000Z","msg":"&quot;民主黨成員林子健前年涉嫌訛稱被人<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">擄走</span></span></strong>，又稱遭毆打及以釘書機釘大腿。&quot;<br />\n&quot;調查警員曾供稱，翻看過前年8月10日收集所得、油麻地砵蘭街一帶的<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">閉路電視片段</span></span></strong>，根據被告的<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">外型、樣貌、衣著及步姿</span></span></strong>追查。&quot;<br />\n&quot;辯方一方則指，被告事發前曾收到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">內地國安部</span></strong></span>名叫「許可」的人發的信息&quot;<br />\n&quot;被告買球衣後於砵蘭街遭兩名中國籍男子挾著他，帶上停泊在砵蘭街的輕型貨車上，其後被拳打顴骨，以及<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被紙巾或毛巾物掩口和鼻後昏迷</span></span></strong>，其後又被綁手腳，以藤條打他及釘書機釘大腿，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再醒來時已在一個石灘</span></span></strong>。&quot;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Ref: <a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2297076/林子健涉虛報被擄走罪成%E3%80%80官指林自編自導自演\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2297076%2F%E6%9E%97%E5%AD%90%E5%81%A5%E6%B6%89%E8%99%9B%E5%A0%B1%E8%A2%AB%E6%93%84%E8%B5%B0%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%25E3%2580%2580%E5%AE%98%E6%8C%87%E6%9E%97%E8%87%AA%E7%B7%A8%E8%87%AA%E5%B0%8E%E8%87%AA%E6%BC%94&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9PtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=baefd83e\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2297076/林子健涉虛報被擄走罪成%E3%80%80官指林自編自導自演</a></span><br />\n<br />\n當年好似都有班人研究左段CCTV好耐，最後不了了之。<br />\n對家一早係呢方法有豐富經驗，所以我覺得大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">除左CCTV外</span></span></strong>，其他野都唔好放過"},{"pid":"f934f991ac21e779551f62cd2ac7f53175527675","tid":1655501,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:55:06.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好拎林子健條on9嚟比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4553ca339c520402fd0cc1196438e053164a13","tid":1655501,"uid":223868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:58:18.000Z","msg":"最後唔係話佢自己作出黎咩 有cctv影到佢失蹤時間喺條街行過"},{"pid":"cabdb3d4947c81dfc52dcb88bb8394c3a37b81fd","tid":1655501,"uid":26270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:06:52.000Z","msg":"你做好research先啦<br />\n唔好放埋一齊比<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"98c43b378228c4a8995b89608f6ac5406c48cb98","tid":1655501,"uid":8562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:17:05.000Z","msg":"請唔好拎條ON9肥仔黎比"},{"pid":"67e166a9b688c2375f82e62712a82824ecc5247c","tid":1655501,"uid":279325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T07:47:10.000Z","msg":"屌你都費事"},{"pid":"c72978f670d323eb18333297ab4b71638f5ff1a5","tid":1655501,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c4553ca339c520402fd0cc1196438e053164a13","tid":1655501,"uid":223868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:58:18.000Z","msg":"最後唔係話佢自己作出黎咩 有cctv影到佢失蹤時間喺條街行過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T00:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v01BiYz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv01BiYz.jpg&h=8f512e8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TB7kLDz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTB7kLDz.jpg&h=9fe42234&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2615b3179b95c9bc17560aa1a7a653f4511d27e7","tid":1655501,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T00:50:24.000Z","msg":"有人講返林子年當時話：<br />\n他說醒來時，發現被人脫去衣服，祗剩下底褲，咁你就明白不用準備衣服啦！"},{"pid":"4646e9841fab2f71f39177b381c98b043a760472","tid":1655501,"uid":48083,"like":0,"disl